This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the datajuicer organization:
- datajuicer/LLaMA-1B-dj-refine-150B tokenizer.json

The bundled `dj-refine-1b` family covers the following official datajuicer models:
- datajuicer/LLaMA-1B-dj-refine-50B
- datajuicer/LLaMA-1B-dj-refine-100B
- datajuicer/LLaMA-1B-dj-refine-150B
- datajuicer/LLaMA-1B-dj-refine-150B-instruct-4.7B

